description: Jamie Knight-Lebel grabs an equaliser for Crewe in their League Two draw at Milton Keynes Dons
title: Milton Keynes Dons 1-1 Crewe Alexandra
title_page: Milton Keynes Dons 1-1 Crewe Alexandra - BBC Sport
maintext:
MK Dons have won three of their last four Football League games against Crewe (L1), as many wins as in their previous nine such encounters (D1 L5).
Crewe are looking to avoid losing on three successive trips to MK Dons in the Football League for the first time since September 2014.
MK Dons have won their final league game of a calendar year on six of the last eight occasions (D1 L1), including a 2-0 win over Crawley Town last year.
Crewe have lost just one of their last six league games that have been their final game of the year (W3 D2), drawing 1-1 with Newport County in 2023.
